    "longBusinessSummary": "Power Generation Joint Stock Corporation 3, together with its subsidiaries, generates and trades in electricity from natural gas, coal dust, thermal, solar, and hydro power plants in Vietnam. The company is involved in the investment and management of investment capital in power generation projects, solar energy, and renewable energy projects; management, operation, repair, maintenance, overhaul, testing, adjustment, renovation, and upgrade of electrical, mechanical, control, and automation equipment in electricity production lines and electrical works; electrical experiments; and electrical mechanics. It also engages in the management, operation, repair, and exploitation of seaports; project management consulting, construction investment project bidding consulting, and estimating; consulting, verification, and supervision of construction and synchronous power grid projects of power generation projects; and consulting on production preparation activities for power plants. In addition, the company is involved in training and developing human resources in operation management, maintenance, and repair of power plant equipment. Further, it engages in the refurbishing and manufacturing of spare parts. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. Power Generation Joint Stock Corporation 3 is a subsidiary of Vietnam Power Group.",
